### HOW TO STYLE ROUNDCUBE FOR FEMINISTWIKI

Creating a new skin is too annoying, even using the "extend" functionality.

Much easier to just copy an existing one and modify a few files.

This is how you can turn the default 'elastic' skin into a FeministMail skin:

- Copy fw-favicon.ico to skins/elastic/images/favicon.ico.

- Copy fw-watermark.png, fw-rounded.png and fw-font.png to skins/elastic/images.

- Modify the following files to point to the FeministWiki images:

  - skins/elastic/templates/login.html:
    Change 'logo.svg' to 'fw-font.png'

  - skins/elastic/templates/includes/menu.html:
    Change 'logo.svg' to 'fw-rounded.png'

  - skins/elastic/watermark.html:
    Change 'logo.svg' to 'fw-watermark.png'

### END
